strategies demonstrating convergence within 250 iterations per strategy.
This rapid

convergence validates the effectiveness of the Expected Improvement
acquisition function in guiding

parameter space exploration toward optimal regions. The progressive
improvement patterns observed

across evaluations demonstrate successful Gaussian Process learning,
with the optimisation algorithm

effectively building predictive models of hyperparameter performance
relationships.

The parameter space exploration reveals sophisticated 3D landscape
navigation capabilities,

successfully discovering optimal regions across the complex
