These features capture the fundamental concept of "meta" in competitive
gaming - the evolving

optimal strategies within the current game state. The mathematical
formulation ensures that teams

selecting currently effective champions receive higher meta scores,
while the consistency metric penalizes compositions with inconsistent
meta positioning.

