\textbf{Team Target Encoded:} Team effectiveness encoding using
𝑇𝑎𝑟𝑔𝑒𝑡𝐸𝑛𝑐𝑜𝑑𝑒(𝑡𝑒𝑎𝑚) \textbf{Patch target Encoded:} Patch-specific context
using 𝑇𝑎𝑟𝑔𝑒𝑡𝐸𝑛𝑐𝑜𝑑𝑒(𝑝𝑎𝑡𝑐ℎ) \textbf{Split Target Encoded:} Season Context
using 𝑇𝑎𝑟𝑔𝑒𝑡𝐸𝑛𝑐𝑜𝑑𝑒(𝑠𝑝𝑙𝑖𝑡)\\
\textbf{Champion Position Target Encoded:}
𝐶ℎ𝑎𝑚𝑝𝑖𝑜𝑛𝐸𝑛𝑐𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑝𝑜𝑠𝑖𝑡𝑜𝑛(𝑐𝑝𝑜𝑠𝑖𝑡𝑖𝑜𝑛)

48

Target encoding transforms categorical variables into numerical
representations that directly correlate with match outcomes, preserving
predictive information while enabling linear model processing. This
approach is particularly effective for logistic regression models,
providing optimal feature\\
representation for linear decision boundaries.

